{8000}{}{Well, ain'tcha the next wasteland's top gunsmith! I guess I could show you something really special for a mere sum of 3000 caps. Whaddya say?}
{8010}{}{If the preaching justifies the price, then let's start with it, ol' man! [Give him $3000]}
{8020}{}{Damn, it's too much for me right now. But I'll be back later, be sure about it.}
{9000}{}{Well, that's the best investement you ever made @sex@|boy||girl|. Come with me... [Eldridge takes you to the table and starts explaining some things about guns]}
{9010}{}{Well... Thanks for that, Eldridge. I must go now, see you later.}
