{11020}{}{Too bad, I don't have that much on me right now. Maybe some other time then.}
{12000}{}{Yeah, I see you're already skilled with those, so this shouldn't take long. But, as you may already know, the caps shortage is going to kill me one day. How about you get me $3000, and I'll show you everything I know?}
{12010}{}{It wasn't easy to find that many caps... It better be worth it! [Give him $3000]}
{12020}{}{Too bad, I don't have that much on me right now. Maybe some other time then.}
